groundspeak:cache.groundspeak:name: SBUX 44 - Double Shot I
groundspeak:cache.groundspeak:long_description:
I was so excited when I saw this SBUX since someone had just recently commented on there not being any here.

I hope you enjoy it & have a fun time!

This cache is hidden right off of Maple Ave. (123) in Vienna, VA. You can park at the Starbucks parking lot (you don't need to go in at all!). Even closer parking is also available.

The original container was a black magnetic hide-a-key. I recently replaced it with something more weather-resistant but just as magnetic. The container is too small for a pen. So be sure to bring one along. This spot always seems to collect what is blowing in the wind, CITO if you can.

This cache was adopted by NetworkCacher on 12/13/05.



If you geocache in Northern Virginia, please join

to get the most out of Geocaching in our region and share your passion with fellow cachers.
Simply go to www.novago.org for details!
